{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775809751492,"sessionID":"ses_289819b18ffeZtw3FTFq54Ocwf","part":{"id":"prt_d768066400017djgVyMrktfHQh","messageID":"msg_d76805b45001NeTQRVqNqrmNy1","sessionID":"ses_289819b18ffeZtw3FTFq54Ocwf","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_1d96ff60a1f941249e8927c7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 — 设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构\n\n### 1.1 定位\n\n`CodeInterpreter` 是 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的 Custom Resource Definition (CRD)，与 `AgentRuntime` 共享同一 API Group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。它声明式地定义代码解释器沙箱的运行环境模板，是 CodeInterpreter 控制器、client-go 生成代码、CLI/SDK 的类型基础。\n\n与 `AgentRuntime` 的差异：\n- `AgentRuntime` 使用通用 `SandboxTemplate`（直接嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`），面向通用 AI Agent 沙箱\n- `CodeInterpreter` 使用专用 `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`，提供更细粒度的字段（`Image`、`Command`、`Args`、`Resources`、`RuntimeClassName` 等），面向代码解释器场景\n- `CodeInterpreter` 独有 `WarmPoolSize`（预热池大小）和 `AuthMode`（认证模式）字段\n- `CodeInterpreterStatus` 额外包含 `Ready` 布尔字段\n\n### 1.2 包结构\n\nCodeInterpreter 类型定义与 AR-001 共享 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包：\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/\n        ├── doc.go                      # 包文档 + k8s 代码生成标记\n        ├── groupversion_info.go        # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder (controller-runtime 风格)\n        ├── register.go                 # Kind 元数据 + Resource 辅助函数\n        ├── codeinterpreter_types.go    # CodeInterpreter CRD + 共享类型（本变更核心）\n        ├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go # CodeInterpreter 类型测试\n        ├── agent_type.go               # AgentRuntime CRD 类型定义 (AR-001)\n        └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go    # controller-gen object 自动生成\n```\n\n### 1.3 依赖关系\n\n```\nCodeInterpreter 类型定义\n  ├── k8s.io/api/core/v1          (corev1.PodSpec, PullPolicy, EnvVar, ResourceRequirements)\n  ├── k8s.io/apimachinery         (metav1.TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Duration, Condition)\n  ├── sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime (scheme.Builder)\n  │\n  ├──→ make generate              产出 zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n  ├──→ make gen-crd               产出 manifests/charts/base/crds/*.yaml\n  ├──→ make gen-client            产出 client-go/ (Typed Client, Informer, Lister, Fake)\n  └──→ CodeInterpreter Controller 通过 Informer/Lister 消费 CodeInterpreter 资源\n```\n\n### 1.4 代码生成工具链\n\n| 工具 | 版本 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| controller-gen | v0.17.2 | DeepCopy 方法生成 + CRD YAML 生成 |\n| k8s.io/code-generator | v0.34.1 | client-go 代码生成 (Typed Client, Informer, Lister, Fake) |\n\n生成入口：`make gen-all` → `generate` + `gen-client`。\n\n---\n\n## 2. 数据结构\n\n### 2.1 包声明与代码生成标记 (`doc.go`)\n\n```go\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1\n```\n\n### 2.2 GroupVersion 与 Scheme (`groupversion_info.go`)\n\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\nimport (\n    \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme\"\n)\n\nvar (\n    GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n    SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n    AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n)\n```\n\n### 2.3 Kind 元数据 (`register.go`)\n\n```go\nvar (\n    CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n    CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n\n    AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n    AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n    AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n)\n\nvar SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n\nfunc Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n    return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n}\n```\n\n### 2.4 共享类型 (`codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n\n以下类型被 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter` 共同使用：\n\n```go\n// ProtocolType 定义端口协议\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\n// AuthModeType 定义认证模式\ntype AuthModeType string\n\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n\n// TargetPort 定义沙箱暴露的端口\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n    Name       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    Port       uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n    Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n```\n\n### 2.5 CodeInterpreter 核心类型 (`codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n\n#### 2.5.1 CodeInterpreter (CR 根类型)\n\n```go\n// +genclient\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n\ntype CodeInterpreter struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n\n    Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**Kubebuilder 标记说明：**\n\n| 标记 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| `+genclient` | 为 client-go 代码生成器标识此类型需要生成 Typed Client |\n| `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | DeepCopy 方法实现 runtime.Object 接口 |\n| `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | 标记为 kubebuilder object root，生成 DeepCopyObject |\n| `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | 启用 `/status` 子资源，分离 spec/status 更新权限 |\n| `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` | 命名空间级资源（REST 复数形式由代码生成器自动推导为 `codeinterpreters`） |\n| `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"...` | `kubectl get codeinterpreters` 输出中显示 Age 列 |\n\n#### 2.5.2 CodeInterpreterSpec\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort                    `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n    Template           *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration                `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration                `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n    WarmPoolSize       *int32                          `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n    AuthMode           AuthModeType                    `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**字段语义：**\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 必填 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|--------|------|\n| `ports` | `[]TargetPort` | 否 | `[]` | 沙箱暴露的端口配置，为空时控制器不配置路由端口 |\n| `template` | `*CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` | 是 | — | 沙箱模板，定义容器镜像、命令、资源等 |\n| `sessionTimeout` | `*metav1.Duration` | 否 | `15m` | 空闲超时后沙箱被清理 |\n| `maxSessionDuration` | `*metav1.Duration` | 否 | `8h` | 沙箱从创建到强制销毁的最大时长 |\n| `warmPoolSize` | `*int32` | 否 | `0` | 预热池大小，控制器维持的空闲沙箱数量 |\n| `authMode` | `AuthModeType` | 否 | `\"\"` (空) | 认证模式：`picod` 或 `none` |\n\n#### 2.5.3 CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels           map[string]string             `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n    Annotations      map[string]string             `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n    RuntimeClassName *string                       `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n    Image            string                        `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n    ImagePullPolicy  corev1.PullPolicy             `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n    ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n    Environment      []corev1.EnvVar               `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n    Command          []string                      `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n    Args             []string                      `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n    Resources        corev1.ResourceRequirements   `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**字段语义：**\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 必填 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|--------|------|\n| `labels` | `map[string]string` | 否 | `{}` | 注入到沙箱 Pod 的额外标签 |\n| `annotations` | `map[string]string` | 否 | `{}` | 注入到沙箱 Pod 的额外注解 |\n| `runtimeClassName` | `*string` | 否 | `nil` | 运行时类名称（如 `kuasar-vmm`），用于指定沙箱运行时 |\n| `image` | `string` | 否 | `\"\"` | 容器镜像 |\n| `imagePullPolicy` | `corev1.PullPolicy` | 否 | `\"\"` | 镜像拉取策略 |\n| `imagePullSecrets` | `[]corev1.LocalObjectReference` | 否 | `[]` | 镜像拉取密钥引用 |\n| `environment` | `[]corev1.EnvVar` | 否 | `[]` | 容器环境变量 |\n| `command` | `[]string` | 否 | `[]` | 容器入口命令 |\n| `args` | `[]string` | 否 | `[]` | 容器入口参数 |\n| `resources` | `corev1.ResourceRequirements` | 否 | `{}` | 容器资源请求和限制 |\n\n**设计决策：** `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` 使用扁平字段而非嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`。\n\n| 方案 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 扁平字段（已选） | CRD YAML 精简；字段语义明确；适合代码解释器场景 | 需手动映射到 PodSpec；不支持 PodSpec 全部能力 |\n| 嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`（AgentRuntime 方案） | 完整 Kubernetes 能力；无需维护字段映射 | CRD YAML 较大（~1000 行）；对代码解释器场景字段过多 |\n\n选择扁平字段的原因：CodeInterpreter 是面向代码解释器的专用 CRD，不需要完整的 PodSpec 能力（如多容器、InitContainer、Volumes 等）。扁平字段使 CRD 更精简、API 更清晰。\n\n#### 2.5.4 CodeInterpreterStatus\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n    Ready      bool               `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**字段语义：**\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `conditions` | `[]metav1.Condition` | 资源状态条件列表 |\n| `ready` | `bool` | 快捷就绪标志，控制器根据 conditions 聚合计算 |\n\n**预期 Condition 类型（由 CodeInterpreter 控制器写入）：**\n\n| Type | Status | Reason | 说明 |\n|------|--------|--------|------|\n| `Ready` | `True` | `SandboxRunning` | 沙箱已成功创建并运行 |\n| `Ready` | `False` | `SandboxFailed` | 沙箱创建失败或异常终止 |\n| `Ready` | `Unknown` | `Pending` | 沙箱正在创建中 |\n\n#### 2.5.5 CodeInterpreterList\n\n```go\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n\ntype CodeInterpreterList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n}\n```\n\n### 2.6 数据结构关系图\n\n```\nCodeInterpreter\n├── TypeMeta (apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, kind: CodeInterpreter)\n├── ObjectMeta (name, namespace, labels, annotations, uid, creationTimestamp, ...)\n├── Spec: CodeInterpreterSpec\n│   ├── ports: []TargetPort\n│   │   ├── pathPrefix: string (optional)\n│   │   ├── name: string (optional)\n│   │   ├── port: uint32 (required)\n│   │   └── protocol: ProtocolType (enum: HTTP|HTTPS)\n│   ├── template: *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate (required)\n│   │   ├── labels: map[string]string (optional)\n│   │   ├── annotations: map[string]string (optional)\n│   │   ├── runtimeClassName: *string (optional)\n│   │   ├── image: string (optional)\n│   │   ├── imagePullPolicy: corev1.PullPolicy (optional)\n│   │   ├── imagePullSecrets: []corev1.LocalObjectReference (optional)\n│   │   ├── environment: []corev1.EnvVar (optional)\n│   │   ├── command: []string (optional)\n│   │   ├── args: []string (optional)\n│   │   └── resources: corev1.ResourceRequirements (optional)\n│   ├── sessionTimeout: *metav1.Duration (default: \"15m\")\n│   ├── maxSessionDuration: *metav1.Duration (default: \"8h\")\n│   ├── warmPoolSize: *int32 (default: 0)\n│   └── authMode: AuthModeType (enum: picod|none)\n└── Status: CodeInterpreterStatus\n    ├── conditions: []metav1.Condition (optional)\n    │   └── {type, status, reason, message, lastTransitionTime, observedGeneration}\n    └── ready: bool (optional)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. API 契约\n\n### 3.1 GroupVersionKind (GVK)\n\n| 组件 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| API Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| Version | `v1alpha1` |\n| Kind | `CodeInterpreter` |\n| ListKind | `CodeInterpreterList` |\n\n### 3.2 GroupVersionResource (GVR)\n\n| 组件 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| Version | `v1alpha1` |\n| Resource | `codeinterpreters` |\n| Scope | Namespaced |\n\n### 3.3 REST API 端点\n\nKubernetes API Server 自动暴露以下端点：\n\n| Method | Path | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `POST` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters` | 创建 CodeInterpreter |\n| `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{name}` | 获取单个 CodeInterpreter |\n| `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters` | 列出命名空间下的 CodeInterpreter |\n| `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/codeinterpreters` | 列出所有命名空间的 CodeInterpreter |\n| `PUT` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{name}` | 更新 CodeInterpreter (spec) |\n| `PATCH` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{name}` | 补丁更新 |\n| `DELETE` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{name}` | 删除 CodeInterpreter |\n| `PUT` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{name}/status` | 更新 status 子资源 |\n\n### 3.4 示例 YAML\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\nkind: CodeInterpreter\nmetadata:\n  name: python-interpreter\n  namespace: default\nspec:\n  ports:\n    - name: web\n      port: 8080\n      protocol: HTTP\n      pathPrefix: /\n  template:\n    labels:\n      app: code-interpreter\n    annotations:\n      agentcube.io/runtime: python-3.11\n    runtimeClassName: kuasar-vmm\n    image: python:3.11-slim\n    imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n    command:\n      - python\n      - \"-m\"\n      - http.server\n    args:\n      - \"8080\"\n    resources:\n      requests:\n        cpu: \"100m\"\n        memory: \"128Mi\"\n      limits:\n        cpu: \"1\"\n        memory: \"512Mi\"\n  sessionTimeout: \"15m\"\n  maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"\n  warmPoolSize: 3\n  authMode: picod\n```\n\n### 3.5 Scheme 注册\n\nCodeInterpreter 类型通过 `SchemeBuilder` 注册到 `runtime.Scheme`：\n\n```go\nfunc init() {\n    SchemeBuilder.Register(&CodeInterpreter{}, &CodeInterpreterList{})\n}\n```\n\n下游组件（CodeInterpreter Controller、client-go fake client）通过调用 `v1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)` 将类型注册到自身 scheme。\n\n### 3.6 生成的 client-go 接口\n\n`make gen-client` 基于本类型定义生成以下接口（详见 `deployment/client-go.md`）：\n\n| 接口 | 方法 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `CodeInterpreterInterface` | `Create`, `Update`, `UpdateStatus`, `Delete`, `Get`, `List`, `Watch`, `Patch` | Typed REST 客户端 |\n| `CodeInterpreterInformer` | `Informer()`, `Lister()` | 共享 Informer + Lister |\n| `CodeInterpreterLister` | `List(selector)`, `CodeInterpreters(namespace)` | 只读缓存索引 |\n| `CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister` | `List(selector)`, `Get(name)` | 命名空间级只读索引 |\n| `FakeCodeInterpreter` | 同上 | 内存测试双端 |\n\n---\n\n## 4. 错误处理\n\n### 4.1 验证错误\n\nKubernetes API Server 在资源创建/更新时自动执行 kubebuilder 标记定义的验证：\n\n| 场景 | 验证标记 | 预期错误 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| `template` 缺失 | 隐式 (Go 零值检查) | 控制器层拦截，返回应用层错误 |\n| `protocol` 非法值 | 无显式 Enum 标记（由应用层校验） | 控制器层拦截 |\n| `authMode` 非法值 | 无显式 Enum 标记（由应用层校验） | 控制器层拦截 |\n| `sessionTimeout` 格式错误 | 隐式 (metav1.Duration 解析) | `422 Unprocessable Entity`: 解析失败 |\n| `warmPoolSize` 负值 | 无显式 Minimum 标记 | 控制器层拦截 |\n\n### 4.2 应用层错误\n\nCodeInterpreter 控制器应定义以下错误类型：\n\n| 错误 | 触发场景 | HTTP 状态码 |\n|------|----------|-------------|\n| `ErrCodeInterpreterNotFound` | 查找不存在的 CodeInterpreter | 404 |\n| `ErrTemplateMissing` | CodeInterpreter 的 `template` 为 nil | 400 |\n| `ErrInvalidAuthMode` | `authMode` 不是 `picod` 或 `none` | 400 |\n| `ErrInvalidWarmPoolSize` | `warmPoolSize` 为负值 | 400 |\n| `ErrInvalidPort` | `ports` 中端口号为 0 或超出范围 | 400 |\n\n### 4.3 默认值处理\n\n| 字段 | 默认值 | 应用时机 |\n|------|--------|----------|\n| `sessionTimeout` | `15m` | 控制器在 reconcile 时注入（或 CRD default） |\n| `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` | 同上 |\n| `warmPoolSize` | `0` | Go 零值（nil 指针视为 0） |\n| `authMode` | `\"\"` (空) | Go 零值，控制器根据场景选择默认认证模式 |\n| `ports` | `[]` (空切片) | Go 零值，无需注入 |\n| `template.imagePullPolicy` | `\"\"` (空) | Go 零值，Kubernetes 默认 `IfNotPresent` |\n\n### 4.4 并发安全\n\n本包定义的类型本身无状态，不涉及并发。类型实例的并发安全由使用者（Informer cache、CodeInterpreter Controller）保证：\n\n- Informer 缓存通过 `cache.SharedIndexInformer` 的 RWMutex 保证读写安全\n- DeepCopy 方法确保跨 goroutine 传递时进行值拷贝\n\n---\n\n## 5. 测试策略\n\n### 5.1 单元测试\n\n#### 5.1.1 常量测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestProtocolTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n    assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"HTTP\"), ProtocolTypeHTTP)\n    assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"HTTPS\"), ProtocolTypeHTTPS)\n}\n\nfunc TestAuthModeTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n    assert.Equal(t, AuthModeType(\"picod\"), AuthModePicoD)\n    assert.Equal(t, AuthModeType(\"none\"), AuthModeNone)\n}\n```\n\n#### 5.1.2 TargetPort 默认值测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestTargetPortDefaults(t *testing.T) {\n    tp := TargetPort{Port: 8080}\n\n    assert.Equal(t, uint32(8080), tp.Port)\n    assert.Empty(t, tp.PathPrefix)\n    assert.Empty(t, tp.Name)\n    assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"\"), tp.Protocol)\n}\n```\n\n#### 5.1.3 CodeInterpreterSpec 默认值测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestCodeInterpreterSpecDefaults(t *testing.T) {\n    ci := &CodeInterpreterSpec{\n        Template: &CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate{},\n    }\n\n    assert.Empty(t, ci.Ports)\n    assert.Nil(t, ci.SessionTimeout)\n    assert.Nil(t, ci.MaxSessionDuration)\n    assert.Nil(t, ci.WarmPoolSize)\n    assert.Equal(t, AuthModeType(\"\"), ci.AuthMode)\n}\n```\n\n#### 5.1.4 DeepCopy 隔离测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestCodeInterpreterSandboxTemplateDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n    runtimeClass := \"kuasar-vmm\"\n    original := &CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate{\n        Labels:           map[string]string{\"app\": \"test\"},\n        Annotations:      map[string]string{\"key\": \"value\"},\n        RuntimeClassName: &runtimeClass,\n        Image:            \"python:3.11\",\n        ImagePullPolicy:  corev1.PullIfNotPresent,\n        Command:          []string{\"python\", \"-m\", \"http.server\"},\n        Args:             []string{\"8080\"},\n    }\n\n    cp := original.DeepCopy()\n\n    assert.Equal(t, original.Image, cp.Image)\n    assert.Equal(t, original.Labels[\"app\"], cp.Labels[\"app\"])\n    assert.Equal(t, *original.RuntimeClassName, *cp.RuntimeClassName)\n\n    cp.Labels[\"app\"] = \"modified\"\n    assert.Equal(t, \"test\", original.Labels[\"app\"])\n\n    cp.Image = \"modified:latest\"\n    assert.Equal(t, \"python:3.11\", original.Image)\n}\n\nfunc TestCodeInterpreterDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n    original := &CodeInterpreter{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test-ci\", Namespace: \"default\"},\n        Spec: CodeInterpreterSpec{\n            Ports: []TargetPort{{Name: \"web\", Port: 8080, Protocol: ProtocolTypeHTTP}},\n            Template: &CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate{\n                Labels: map[string]string{\"app\": \"test\"},\n                Image:  \"python:3.11\",\n            },\n            SessionTimeout:     &metav1.Duration{Duration: 15 * time.Minute},\n            MaxSessionDuration: &metav1.Duration{Duration: 8 * time.Hour},\n            WarmPoolSize:       ptrInt32(3),\n            AuthMode:           AuthModePicoD,\n        },\n        Status: CodeInterpreterStatus{Ready: true},\n    }\n\n    cp := original.DeepCopy()\n\n    assert.Equal(t, original.Name, cp.Name)\n    assert.Equal(t, original.Spec.WarmPoolSize, cp.Spec.WarmPoolSize)\n    assert.Equal(t, original.Spec.AuthMode, cp.Spec.AuthMode)\n    assert.Equal(t, original.Status.Ready, cp.Status.Ready)\n\n    cp.Spec.WarmPoolSize = ptrInt32(5)\n    assert.Equal(t, int32(3), *original.Spec.WarmPoolSize)\n}\n\nfunc TestCodeInterpreterListDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n    original := &CodeInterpreterList{\n        ListMeta: metav1.ListMeta{ResourceVersion: \"5678\"},\n        Items: []CodeInterpreter{\n            {ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"ci1\", Namespace: \"default\"}},\n        },\n    }\n\n    cp := original.DeepCopy()\n\n    assert.Equal(t, original.ListMeta.ResourceVersion, cp.ListMeta.ResourceVersion)\n    assert.Equal(t, len(original.Items), len(cp.Items))\n    assert.Equal(t, original.Items[0].Name, cp.Items[0].Name)\n\n    cp.Items[0].Name = \"modified\"\n    assert.Equal(t, \"ci1\", original.Items[0].Name)\n}\n```\n\n#### 5.1.5 Scheme 注册测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestCodeInterpreterSchemeRegistration(t *testing.T) {\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    err := v1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n\n    gvk := v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n    obj, err := scheme.New(gvk)\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.IsType(t, &v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{}, obj)\n\n    gvkList := v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreterList\")\n    objList, err := scheme.New(gvkList)\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.IsType(t, &v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList{}, objList)\n}\n```\n\n### 5.2 测试文件布局\n\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n├── codeinterpreter_types.go         # CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go    # CodeInterpreter 类型测试\n├── agent_type.go                    # AgentRuntime 类型定义 (AR-001)\n├── agent_type_test.go               # AgentRuntime 类型测试 (AR-001)\n├── groupversion_info.go             # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder\n├── groupversion_info_test.go        # Scheme 注册测试\n├── register.go                      # Kind 元数据\n├── register_test.go                 # GVK/GVR 常量测试\n└── zz_generated.deepcopy.go         # 自动生成\n```\n\n### 5.3 测试运行\n\n```bash\n# 运行 pkg/apis 下所有测试\ngo test ./pkg/apis/... -v\n\n# 运行带覆盖率\ngo test ./pkg/apis/... -coverprofile=coverage.out\ngo tool cover -html=coverage.out\n```\n\n### 5.4 TDD 关联\n\n本变更与 TDD 规范的关联用例：\n\n| TDD 用例 | 关联 | 说明 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| TestCase-CI-001 | 直接 | CodeInterpreter 类型是沙箱创建接口的输入基础 |\n| TestCase-CI-002 | 直接 | WarmPool 预热逻辑依赖 `warmPoolSize` 字段 |\n| TestCase-CI-003 | 直接 | 认证模式路由依赖 `authMode` 字段 |\n\n---\n\n## 6. 实现步骤\n\n### 6.1 文件创建顺序\n\n1. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` — CodeInterpreter 核心类型 + 共享类型\n2. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types_test.go` — 类型测试\n3. 运行 `make generate` — 更新 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n4. 运行 `make gen-client` — 生成 client-go 代码（Typed Client, Informer, Lister, Fake）\n\n### 6.2 验证检查清单\n\n- [ ] `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n- [ ] `make generate` 成功更新 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n- [ ] `git diff --exit-code` 通过（生成文件无意外变更）\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreter` GVK = `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, Kind=CodeInterpreter`\n- [ ] GVR resource = `codeinterpreters`\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` 使用扁平字段而非嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`\n- [ ] `WarmPoolSize` 字段类型为 `*int32`\n- [ ] `AuthMode` 字段类型为 `AuthModeType`\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreterStatus` 包含 `Ready` 布尔字段\n- [ ] `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` 已添加\n- [ ] `+kubebuilder:printcolumn` Age 列已添加\n- [ ] `go test ./pkg/apis/...` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## 7. 后续变更\n\n本变更完成后，以下变更可并行开展：\n\n| 变更 | 依赖关系 | 说明 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| CRD YAML 生成 | 依赖 AR-002 | `make gen-crd` 从 kubebuilder 标记产出 CodeInterpreter CRD YAML |\n| client-go 生成 | 依赖 AR-002 | `make gen-client` 产出 CodeInterpreter Typed Client/Informer/Lister/Fake |\n| CodeInterpreter Controller | 依赖 client-go 生成 | 通过 Informer/Lister 消费 CodeInterpreter 资源，管理沙箱生命周期 |\n| WarmPool 预热控制器 | 依赖 AR-002 | 根据 `warmPoolSize` 维持空闲沙箱池 |\n| 认证路由 | 依赖 AR-002 | 根据 `authMode` 配置沙箱认证方式 |\n| CLI/SDK CodeInterpreter 命令 | 依赖 AR-002 | 提供 `codeinterpreter create/get/list/delete` 命令 |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibab